OCCIDENTAL BASKETBALL TEAMS TO OPEN SEASONS 
The Occidental College men's and women's basketball teams will open their 
seasons tonight in a doubleheader at Occidental. 
The women's team, led by Sharon Wada -- a two-time All-Southern California 
Intercollegiate Athletic Conference guard -- will play host to UC San Diego at 
6 p.m. 
All-SCIAC center Chris Anderson and all-conference forward John Crawley will 
lead the men's team against Biola at 8. GARY KLEIN 
